{
  "$schema": "https://openapi.vercel.sh/vercel.json",
  "framework": "nextjs",
  "buildCommand": "next build",
  "installCommand": "npm install",
  "outputDirectory": ".next",
  "regions": ["gru1"],
  "github": {
    "silent": true
  },
  "_comment": [
    "Demo ficticia: NAO subir pra Vercel real ainda.",
    "Quando deployar:",
    "  1. Importar este diretorio (src/projeto-tech/kore-tech/frontend) na Vercel",
    "  2. Setar Root Directory = src/projeto-tech/kore-tech/frontend",
    "  3. Setar env vars: NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://<railway>.up.railway.app,",
    "     NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://<vercel-frontend>.vercel.app,",
    "     NEXT_PUBLIC_DASHBOARD_URL=https://<vercel-dashboard>.vercel.app,",
    "     NEXT_PUBLIC_WHATSAPP_NUMBER=<numero_real>",
    "  4. Atualizar CSP connect-src em next.config.mjs com host real do backend (licao #05)",
    "  5. Atualizar CORS_ORIGIN no Railway pra incluir esse dominio Vercel"
  ]
}
